properties.headline: FLOODING WILCANNIA TO IVANHOE Cobb Highway CLOSED
properties.diversions:
Southbound from Wilcannia: Barrier Hwy to Cobar, Kidman Way to Goolgowi, and Mid Western Hwy to Hay.

Northbound from Hay: Mid Western Hwy to Goolgowi, Kidman Way to Cobar, and Barrier Hwy to Wilcannia.

This route is suitable for all vehicles and will add around 4hrs to your travel time.

properties.headline: FLOODING ROYAL NATIONAL PARK Audley Weir is closed between Audley Road and Sir Bertram Stevens Drive

properties.headline: FLOODING WALGETT TO BREWARRINA Kamilaroi Highway
properties.otherAdvice: The road is flooded approximately 65km west of Walgett.
properties.diversions:
From Walgett to Bourke: Castlereagh Hwy to Gilgandra, Oxley Hwy to Nevertire, Mitchell Hwy to Bourke.

From Brewarrina to Bourke:: Arthur Hall Vc Way to Coolabah, then Mitchell Hwy to Bourke.


These diversions are suitable for all vehicles.
